description: A dictionary containing all possible entry types (e.g. entryTypes['note']). Most commonly used ones are: note (regular entry), error, file and image
name: entryTypes

description: A dictionary containing all supported values of entry ContentsFormat/ReadableContentsFormat - json, markdown, text, image, html, etc (e.g. formats['markdown'])
name: formats

description: A dictionary containing all supported dbotscore values and their numeric representations - Critical, High, Medium, Low, Unknown and Informational (e.g. dbotscores['High']).
name: dbotscores

description: A dictionary containing commonly used context (output) paths - file, ip url, domain, email, dbotscore (e.g. outputPaths['domain'])
name: outputPaths
